ota]]\n[[Category:Mixed martial artists from South Dakota]]\n[[Category:People from Webster, South Dakota]]\n[[Category:People from Maple Plain, Minnesota]]\n[[Category:Players of American football from South Dakota]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestlers from South Dakota]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Regina, Saskatchewan]]\n[[Category:Ultimate Fighting Championship male fighters]]\n[[Category:Wrestling Observer Newsletter Hall of Fame]]\n[[Category:WWF/WWE World Heavyweight Champions]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American professional wrestler, MMA fighter, and football player}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{pp-semi-blp|small=yes}}\n{{Use American English|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Brock Lesnar\n| image              = Brock Lesnar in March 2015.jpg\n| image_size         =\n| caption            = Lesnar in March 2015\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|mf=yes|1977|7|12}}\n| birth_place        = [[Webster, South Dakota]], U.S.\n| occupation         = Professional wrestler, mixed martial artist, American football player\n| years_active       = 2000\u20132007; 2012\u2013present<br />(wrestling)<br />2004 (football)<br />2007\u20132011; 2016 (MMA)\n| spouse             = {{marriage|[[Sable (wrestler)|Sable]]<br />|May 6, 2006}}\n| children           = 4\n| module             = {{Infobox professional wrestler|child=yes\n|names = Brock Lesnar<ref name=\"SlamBio\">{{cite web|url=http://slam.canoe.com/Slam/Wrestling/Bios/lesnar.html|title=Brock Lesnar Bio|work=Slam! Sports|publisher=[[Canoe.com|Canadian Online Explorer]]|first1 =John|last1=Milner|first2=Frederik|last2=Heinen|accessdate=March 9, 2019}}</ref>\n|height = 6 ft 3 in<ref name=\"WWEbio\">{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/superstars/brock-lesnar|title=Brock Lesnar bio|publisher=[[WWE]]|accessdate=August 7, 2015}}</ref>\n|weight = 286 lb<ref name=\"WWEbio\"/>\n|residence = [[Maryfield, Saskatchewan]], Canada\n|billed = [[Minneapolis|Minn